<h2>Important Notes</h2>

<p>Bit Bazaar is a small community event. We expect 500-750 attendees throughout the day.</p>
<p>The event is held at <a href="http://goo.gl/maps/jTmW8">Bento Miso</a>, in Toronto's Queen West neighborhood.</p>
<p>We do not have any refrigerator space available during the event, but you will have access to a sink and one power outlet.</p>
<p>To adhere to local bylaws, selected food vendors must be able to provide proof of:</p>
<ul class="">
  <li>Municipal Food Handler certification</li>
  <li>Use of licensed commercial kitchen (your own or a rented facility) to prepare the food</li>
  <li>Insurance on your products</li>
</ul>





